name: Messenger
body:
### Why a new library?!
I had to code some sort of WebRtc library for university (UT Vienna). I tried to create a messaging platform for dart, but the main purpose is to setup a WebRTC datachannel.

### Status
This project is not finished yet.

### Authors and Contributors
@inkrement

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with this library? Just create a new Issue report!
